name: Fauna Flowers 09 - Tartaruga Flower
description:
Not just another brick in the garden. The most wise and long-lived flower in the garden. You have to be patient with this one, because it grows at a very slow pace. A flower that can live together with all the animals and plants of the forest. If you don`t like this one... the shame is on you.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
